data.description: Stunning and move in ready with a spacious and open floor plan is the perfect description! 4 bedrooms, spacious with a peaceful view overlooking the pond is what awaits you. Large bright tile throughout the home and super clean carpets in the bedrooms. Like cooking or entertaining? The kitchen has a large island for all of your entertaining needs. New roof installed 2023 and has a 10 year transferable warranty. A/C regularly serviced. Garage has epoxy floors and a wall mounted mini split that cools and is energy efficient. Exterior of the home has an extended brick driveway and sidewalks along the sides along that extend to the rear patio. Low HOA. Personally view this home and start planning!
